subject: Boxing
lead_paragraph: The light welterweight Frankie Gomez won a close bout against Gyula Kate of Hungary at the world championships in Milan. Gomez, the only remaining American, advanced to the championship match against the Olympic bronze medalist Roniel Iglesias of Cuba. Gomez landed a jab in the closing moments to pull out an 8-7 victory.
